TI  - A Study of the Relationship Between Toxin Levels in the Elkhorn Slough and Moss Landing State Beach
PY  - 1997
PB  - University of California, Berkeley
UR  - https://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~pkmendez/envsci/projects/1997final/AllenJ_1997.pdf
