TI  - PART I ENVIRONMENTAL ECONOMICS, POLICY & EDUCATION
PY  - 1997
PB  - University of California, Berkeley
UR  - https://www.ocf.berkeley.edu/~pkmendez/envsci/projects/1997final/RabinovichA_1997.pdf
